    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要先验证地址。我们加一个CheckAddress的判断节点，如果地址无效就走到错误处理，有效的话进入准备交易环节。这个判断节点还是放在Education_LMS_Portal里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckAddress",
        "ErrorInvalidAddress",
        "PrepareTransaction"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了CheckAddress判断节点，分出No和Yes两条路径。No指向ErrorInvalidAddress，Yes指向PrepareTransaction。路径标签需要标注吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckAddress",
        "ErrorInvalidAddress",
        "PrepareTransaction"
